videos.description: Tony Pollard breaks free for a 58-yard rushing touchdown on the reverse to put Memphis up 7-0.
videos.headline: Memphis scores 58-yard touchdown on trick play

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play Video (Memphis scores 58-yard touchdown on trick play) 20171027 ESHEET

videos.description: Riley Ferguson finds Anthony Miller for a 16-yard touchdown, his 10th receiving touchdown of the season and second most in FBS.
videos.headline: Ferguson, Miller give Memphis a two-touchdown lead

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ferguson, Miller give Memphis a two-touchdown lead) 20171027 ESHEET

videos.description: Riley Ferguson connects with his tight end, Sean Dykes for a 38-yard touchdown to give Memphis a 21-0 lead in the first half.
videos.headline: Dykes gets separation for TD

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Dykes gets separation for TD) 20171027 ESHEET

videos.description: Darrell Henderson finds a hole for an 82-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: 82-yard TD widens Memphis' lead

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (82-yard TD widens Memphis' lead) 20171027 ESHEET

videos.description: Riley Ferguson throws his third touchdown pass, this time to Kedarian Jones for a 37-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Memphis' offense continues to roll

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Memphis' offense continues to roll) 2017/10/27 ESHEET

videos.description: Nathan Banks fakes the handoff and rushes into the end zone for a 4-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Banks scores Tulane's first TD

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Banks scores Tulane's first TD) 20171027 ESHEET

videos.description: Riley Ferguson evades the sack, but his pass is intercepted by Jarrod Franklin.
videos.headline: Tulane picks off Ferguson

videos.description: Jonathan Banks throws a 7-yard touchdown pass to Charles Jones II, but could not convert the two-point conversion as Tulane trails 35-12 at halftime.
videos.headline: Tulane scores with 7 seconds left in first half

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tulane scores with 7 seconds left in first half) 20171027 ESHEET

videos.description: Jonathan Banks finds Charles Jones II open in the end zone on 4th-and-goal for a 6-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Tulane converts on 4th down

videos.description: Memphis forces its 21st turnover of the season, and Austin Hall recovers in the end zone to put Memphis up 42-19 against Tulane.
videos.headline: Memphis forces fumble for TD

videos.description: Jonathan Banks finds a wide open Darnell Mooney for a 41-yard touchdown, but Tulane trails 42-26 in the fourth.
videos.headline: Mooney grabs a 41-yard TD

videos.description: Riley Ferguson rushes for a 1-yard touchdown, his fourth touchdown of the game.
videos.headline: Ferguson goes over the top for 4th TD
